n the Participation of Young People in Local and Regional Life|url=https://books.google.ru/books?id=yimsy89V9YIC&pg=PA47 |location=[[Krakow]] |publisher=[[Council of Europe]] |page=38 |isbn=9287153744}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://search.coe.int/cm/Pages/result_details.aspx?ObjectID=09000016805e1d2f |title=Advisory Council of the European Youth Centre and the European Youth Foundation (DJS/CC), Abridged report of the 8th meeting (Strasbourg, 29-30 September 2002), CM(2002)143 |publisher=[[Council of Europe]] |date=2002-10-16|access-date=2020-05-03}}</ref>\n|{{Flag|France}}\n|World Organization of the Scout Movement (WOSM)\n|-\n|1999-2000\n|Guillaume L\u00e9gaut<ref name=\"1stAC\"/>\n|{{Flag|France}}\n|World Organization of the Scout Movement (WOSM)\n|}\n\n== External links ==\n{{Commons category|Advisory Council on Youth of the Council of Europe|Advisory Council on Youth}}\n* [https://www.coe.int/en/web/youth/advisory-council-on-youth Advisory Council on Youth] at the website of the [[Council of Europe]]\n* [https://rm.coe.int/16809991e4 Terms of reference] of the Advisory Council on Youth (PDF; 72 KB)\n* {{Facebook}}\n* {{Twitter}}\n* {{Instagram}}\n* [https://rm.coe.int/1680702423 2014 Info leaflet] of the Advisory Council on Youth (PDF; 2.2 MB)\n\n== References ==\n<references/>\n\n[[Category:Youth organizations based in Europe|Advisory Council on Youth]]\n[[Category:Council of Europe|Advisory Council on Youth]]\n", "name_user": "Rosso Robot", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eChairpersons:-typo", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Advisory_Council_on_Youth"}
